\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces ODE posterior under uniform-network data (blue) sits near its reference $\beta _{mf,true}$; posterior under community-network data (red) concentrates well to the left of its reference (dashed black line), demonstrating systematic bias. Both posteriors are tight---the bias is not uncertainty, it is misspecification.}}{4}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:bias_single}{{1}{4}{ODE posterior under uniform-network data (blue) sits near its reference $\beta _{mf,true}$; posterior under community-network data (red) concentrates well to the left of its reference (dashed black line), demonstrating systematic bias. Both posteriors are tight---the bias is not uncertainty, it is misspecification}{figure.1}{}}
